<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" defer></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="CUSTOMER/about.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CUSTOMER/footer.css">
   
    <title>About Us</title>
</head>

<body onclick="closeMenu()">
    <div class="heading">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="container-1">
        <div class="left-div">
            <h2>Fast and safe delivery</h2>
            
            <p>At our food website, we pride ourselves on our lightning-fast delivery service. From piping hot pizzas to delicious sushi rolls, our experienced drivers will ensure that your food arrives at your doorstep in record time. With real-time tracking updates and a commitment to quality, we guarantee that you'll be enjoying your meal in no time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="right-div">
            <img src="/CUSTOMER/Order_Food/images/abt1.jpeg" alt="">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-2">
        <div class="right-div">
            
            <img src="/CUSTOMER/Order_Food/images/abt2.jpg" alt="">
        </div>
        <div class="left-div">
            <h2>Best restaurants for you</h2>
            
            <p>Looking for the best restaurants in town? Look no further than our food website! We handpick the finest eateries, from cozy cafes to five-star restaurants, to ensure that you have access to the best culinary experiences around. With comprehensive reviews and menus, you'll be able to make an informed choice every time.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-3">
        <div class="left-div">
            <h2>Food recipes</h2>
            
            <p>At our website, we're passionate about all things food! That's why we offer a wide range of recipes for you to explore, from healthy breakfasts to indulgent desserts. Whether you're an experienced cook or just starting out, our easy-to-follow recipes and step-by-step instructions will help you create delicious meals every time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="right-div">
            <img src="/CUSTOMER/Order_Food/images/abt3.jpg" alt="">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-4 mb-4">
        <div class="right-div">
            <img src="/CUSTOMER/Order_Food/images/abt4.jpg" alt="">
        </div>
        <div class="left-div">
            <h2>Food donation</h2>
            
            <p>At our website, we believe that everyone has a role to play in reducing food waste and fighting hunger. That's why we encourage restaurants to partner with us and donate surplus food to local charities and food banks. By working together, we can make a real difference in our communities and help ensure that no one goes hungry.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-5 mt-4 mb-4">
        <div class="feed-btn">
            <button type="button" class="btn" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#myModal">Write Us Feedback</button>
        </div>
       
        <div class="modal fade" id="myModal">
            <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg modal-dialog-centered modal-dialog-scrollable">
              <div class="modal-content">
          
                <!-- Modal Header -->
                <div class="modal-header">
                  <h4>Feedback</h4>
                  <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
                </div>
          
                <!-- Modal body -->
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <% if(currentUser){%>
                        <form action="/submitUserFeedback" method="post">
                            <div>
                                <label for="mobile">Your Mobile Number :</label>
                                <input type="text" name="mobileNumber" id="mobile" class="form-control form-control-lg mt-1" placeholder="<%=currentUser.mobileNumber%>" disabled><br>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mt-2 mb-4">
                                <label for="feedback">Feedback : </label>
                                <textarea name="feedback" id="feedback" cols="30" rows="5" class="form-control form-control-lg mt-1" placeholder="Write Your Feedback Here..."></textarea>
                           </div>
                           <div class="feed-submit mt-4 mb-4">
                                <button  type="submit" class="btn" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Submit Feedback</a>
                           </div>
                        </form>
                 
                   <%}else{%>
                    <h4>Please Login to Continue!</h4>
                    <%}%>
                </div>
          
               
                
          
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
    </div>
    <%- include('../partials/footer.ejs') %>
</body>

</html>